snippet.title: ODDCORE - Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2896260/ODDCORE/

ODDCORE - a retro-inspired boomer shooter packed with endless, brain-rotting fun. You've been employed to protect the core of our memories one variant at a time. Deploy each run with new loadouts, manage time wisely and eradicate the corrupted hordes.

FREE DEMO COMING SOON!

For dev logs, check out our YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/@oddcoregame

Join our Discord for updates:
https://discord.com/invite/4pwUckApJ7

Follow ODDCORE:
https://x.com/oddcoregame
https://www.instagram.com/oddcoregame

#ODDCORE #boomershooter #backrooms
